Bad Return Values

A list of distributions that don't return a valid return statement. You can consider this distributions buggy. This list is further broken down into the type of PPI::Statement class they return. To view the full bad return value, click on the 'show'-link.

  • PPI::Statement (9 dists)
  • PPI::Statement (but very likely crap) (515 dists)
  • PPI::Statement::Break (but very likely crap) (12 dists)
  • PPI::Statement::Compound (64 dists)
  • PPI::Statement::Include (63 dists)
  • PPI::Statement::Package (62 dists)
  • PPI::Statement::Scheduled (29 dists)
  • PPI::Statement::Sub (1126 dists)
  • PPI::Statement::Variable (104 dists)
